I '''Eric Paul Allman''' (mibait Septiembri 2, 1955) metung yang Americanung computer programmer a menalkus keng [[sendmail]] at ing manimuna keng [[delivermail]] inyang bandang tauli ning dekada 1970 ampong mumunana ning dekada 1980 king [[UC Berkeley]].

==Pamagaral ampong sanayan==
MIbait king [[El Cerrito, California]], i Allman balu na ibat pa inyang malati ya na bisa yang magobra keng [[computing]], sepilitan yang lulub kareng [[mainframe]] ning kayang pipagaralan a high school at kaibat ginamit no ring [[computing center]] na ning [[UC Berkeley]] para karing kayang pamangailangan keng computing. Inyang 1973, linub ya king UC Berkeley, inyang magumpisa ya pa ing [[Unix]] operating system kareng keng academia.<ref>{{cite news |first=Andrew |last=Leonard |title=You've got sendmail |url=http://archive.salon.com/21st/feature/1998/12/cov_11feature.html |publisher=Salon.com |accessdate=2007-08-20 }}</ref>  Ikua ne ing kayang B.S. ampong M.S. a kursu ibat UC Berkeley inyang 1977 ampong 1980 king pamituki ra.

